data.description: What an incredible opportunity to live on the Lake! Home is located on the N Shores of Lake Manawa featuring an incredible view of the entire lake. No canal or boat docks stop you from immediate lake access. Home is one of a kind with so many opportunities from personal home with tons of fun or the rare opportunity to Airbnb the property for an investment. Home offers 4 bedrooms ,4 baths, 4 different areas to view your favorite shows. Home comes fully furnished, which is a huge bonus.  As mentioned, an incredible view of the lake from your oversized eat in kitchen or covered deck. Hot tub, patio, green space, shed, boat dock and Jet skis tie ups as you have it all here. 2 car attached garage with off street parking
